<div class="text-left popoverex activitylistneighborhoodgroups"><div class='activitylistneighborhood'>Canoga Park</div><div class="activitylisttitle">Junior Youth Spiritual Empowerment Program <br />(Ages 11-15)</div><div class="activitylistdate">Fri Apr 10 3:00PM</div><div class="activitylistdetails"><a id="tannaz@labahais.org-2015-04-10-15:00-Junior-Youth-Spiritual-Empowerment-Program-(Ages-11-15)" tabindex="0" class="btn btn-blue btn-sm" data-toggle="popover" data-trigger="focus" title="Details" data-html="true" data-content="<p>Two separate junior youth groups meet weekly. They identify social forces around them and plan service projects for the betterment of the community. These service projects are combined with healthy recreation (including cooperative sports and games), a study of Baha&#039;i-inspired texts, and complementary activities organized by the junior youth based on their understanding of the curriculum.</p><p>For more information, please e-mail Tannaz: tannaz@labahais.org</p>">Details</a></div><div class="activitylisttitle">Junior Youth Spiritual Empowerment Program <br />(Ages 11-13) <br />(Ages 14-15)</div><div class="activitylistdate">Fri Apr 10 5:00PM</div><div class="activitylistdetails"><a id="tannaz@labahais.org-2015-04-10-17:00-Junior-Youth-Spiritual-Empowerment-Program-(Ages-11-13)-(Ages-14-15)" tabindex="0" class="btn btn-blue btn-sm" data-toggle="popover" data-trigger="focus" title="Details" data-html="true" data-content="<p>Four separate junior youth groups meet weekly. They identify social forces around them and plan service projects for the betterment of the community. These service projects are combined with healthy recreation (including cooperative sports and games), a study of Baha&#039;i-inspired texts, and complementary activities organized by the junior youth based on their understanding of the curriculum.</p><p>For more information, please e-mail Tannaz: tannaz@labahais.org</p>">Details</a></div></div><div class="text-left popo